name: Vintage Fun Bobby Pin Set
description:
This is a sweet and elegant bobby pin set which will add a lovely vintage accent to your hair. The Vintage Fun set consists of the Nadia and Black Baccara bobby pins, both of which are perfect for both your casual and dressy days!

The Nadia bobby pin is made from a 1960s sewing finding comprising silver/grey acrylic pearls sewn onto a metal disc. This beautiful, vintage love knot is in wonderful condition and measures approximately 22mm (0.9 in) in diameter.
The Black Baccara bobby pin features a vintage Japanese acrylic cabochon in a unique "carved"-looking black rose design. This delightful cabochon measures 18mm (0.7 in) wide.

Both the pearl knot and the black rose have been firmly attached to a silver tone bobby pin base - you will see some glue "squeeze out" on the back of the pin assuring a good strong grip.
Each bobby pin is approximately 55mm (2.2 in) long.

If you are after more than one of these beauties, please convo me for a reserve listing.

name: Glam It Up - Vintage Amethyst Teardrop Jewel Earrings (sterling silver)
description:
These gorgeous earrings are perfect for those occasions when bold and sparkly are the look you need!

The Glam It Up earrings feature stunning 18x13mm (0.7x0.5 in) vintage teardrop glass jewels in a beautiful amethyst purple. These jewels have been set in modern silver-plated pronged settings and dangle from STERLING SILVER ear hooks.

These earrings would look beautiful matched with your little black dress or a matching purple gown. Definitely a gorgeous nod to the vintage glamour of old.

These earrings are approximately 45mm (1.77 in) long.

Please note that these jewels are vintage (1950s) so may show some signs of wear and aging.
Please convo me if you are interested in more than one pair of these beauties.

name: Chocolate Dessert - Feather and Pearl Bracelet
description:
This beautiful and elegant bracelet features a vintage-inspired feather charm as its centrepiece! The feather is flanked by high quality glass pearls in a sumptuous chocolate brown.

This bracelet would be lovely for a bridesmaid or simply to spoil yourself.  This versatile bracelet can also be teamed with more casual outfits!

The Chocolate Dessert bracelet is approximately 19cm (7.5 inches) long and comfortably fits a 16cm wrist.  Please convo me if you need the length altered to suit your wrist as I can remove a link or add an extender chain. Extender chains can be added for an extra AUD$0.40.

name: Tainted Love - Swarovski Crystal Necklace
description:
This pretty and romantic necklace is sure to capture your heart with its delicate beauty!

The pendant consists of a ruby red coloured Swarovski crystal briolette which has been wire wrapped with silver-plated tarnish resistant wire. A jet black Czech glass bead adds a little accent and contrast to the pendant. This ensemble hangs from a delicate, silver-plated chain with a lobster clasp to keep it firmly on.

Despite its name, this necklace would be perfect for your bridesmaid or for a girl going to her prom or debutante ball. This necklace is so versatile it would also look stunning with a casual skirt and tee outfit.

The pendant is approximately 30mm long by 15mm wide (1.2 by 0.6 in) and the necklace chain is approximately 46cm (18 in).

name: Art Print. Peacock. Vintage Dictionary Page.
description:
Peacock art print. Home decor by Two Cheeky Monkeys on Big Cartel.

This is a beautiful inkjet print of a vintage peacock illustration dating from 1869. It has been printed onto a vintage Oxford Dictionary page, creating a unique and beautiful artwork for your walls.
The resplendent peacock is perched on a branch waiting for passers by to shower him with compliments.  As each dictionary page is different, you will not receive this exact print, but it will be very similar.

The print is 5x7 inch in size and comes with YOUR CHOICE of a black or white photo mat. The finished size of the print and mat is 8x10 inches. Because the dictionary page is thin and delicate, the print has been backed with archival quality paper which matches the cream colour of the dictionary page. This print is perfect for those who adore the beauty of the peacock or for those with an ornithology bent!

♦ PLEASE STATE IN THE NOTES TO SELLER WHETHER YOU WANT A BLACK OR WHITE PHOTO MAT. ♦

♥ Looking for an art print with a different illustration? Please contact me and I will see which of my images meet your needs! ♥
